  <description type="morphology">Distal leaves long-subulate beyond an ovate, obovate, or broadly elliptic base, 1–3.2 mm, leaf base strongly differentiated in shape; distal laminal cells long-rectangular.  Sexual condition autoicous.  Seta 0.2–0.7 mm.  Capsule neck short, broadly obovate to truncate.  Spores reticulate.  Calyptra smooth.</description>
  <description type="morphology">Capsules mature spring.</description>
